      • publish

        public void publish(ClusterChangedEvent clusterChangedEvent,
                    Discovery.AckListener ackListener)
        Publish all the changes to the cluster from the master (can be called just by the master). The publish process should not publish this state to the master as well! (the master is sending it...).

        The Discovery.AckListener allows to acknowledge the publish event based on the response gotten from all nodes
